Package me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job

Class JobActivity

java.lang.Object
me.marcosassuncao.servsim.job.JobActivity
public class JobActivity extends Object
This class is used to keep track of the work carried out by resources when executing a job that is preempted.
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
